    <div class="highlight-box"><strong>Key fact:</strong> Alcohol contains 7 kcal per gram — almost as calorie-dense as fat (9 kcal/g). Unlike fat and protein, alcohol has no nutritional value and is processed by the liver as a priority over fat metabolism, effectively pausing fat burning while alcohol is in your system.</div>
